---
layout: layouts/tool.njk
title: Word Counter - Count Words, Characters & Sentences Online
description: Free online word counter tool. Count words, characters, sentences, paragraphs instantly. Get reading time and speaking time estimates. No signup required.
keywords: word counter, character count, word count online, character counter, sentence counter, reading time calculator, speaking time
permalink: /tools/word-counter/
toolId: word-counter
toolJs: word-counter.js
ogImage: word-counter.jpg
---
{% set toolData = tools | findById(toolId) %}

{% block schema %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "{{ site.url }}/"},
    {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Tools", "item": "{{ site.url }}/#tools"},
    {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "{{ toolData.name }}", "item": "{{ site.url }}{{ page.url }}"}
  ]
}
</script>
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "WebApplication",
  "name": "{{ toolData.fullName }}",
  "description": "{{ description }}",
  "url": "{{ site.url }}{{ page.url }}",
  "applicationCategory": "UtilityApplication",
  "operatingSystem": "Any",
  "browserRequirements": "Requires JavaScript",
  "offers": {"@type": "Offer", "price": "0", "priceCurrency": "USD"},
  "featureList": ["Word count", "Character count with/without spaces", "Sentence count", "Paragraph count", "Reading time estimate", "Speaking time estimate"],
  "author": {"@type": "Organization", "name": "{{ site.name }}", "url": "{{ site.url }}"}
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

{% block head %}
<style>
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }
  .stat-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-4);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-card-value {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-card-label {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-top: var(--space-1);
  }
  .word-input {
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 300px;
    padding: var(--space-4);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    resize: vertical;
  }
  .word-input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px var(--color-primary-light);
  }
  .time-estimates {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }
  .time-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
  .time-value {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
</style>
{% endblock %}

<div class="tool-container">
  <!-- Stats Grid -->
  <div class="stats-grid">
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-card-value" id="word-count">0</div>
      <div class="stat-card-label">Words</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-card-value" id="char-count">0</div>
      <div class="stat-card-label">Characters</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-card-value" id="char-no-space">0</div>
      <div class="stat-card-label">Characters (no spaces)</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-card-value" id="sentence-count">0</div>
      <div class="stat-card-label">Sentences</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-card-value" id="paragraph-count">0</div>
      <div class="stat-card-label">Paragraphs</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-card">
      <div class="stat-card-value" id="line-count">0</div>
      <div class="stat-card-label">Lines</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Text Input -->
  <textarea
    id="text-input"
    class="word-input"
    placeholder="Start typing or paste your text here..."
    aria-label="Text input for word counting"
  ></textarea>

  <!-- Time Estimates -->
  <div class="time-estimates">
    <div class="time-item">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/>
      </svg>
      <span>Reading time:</span>
      <span class="time-value" id="reading-time">0 min</span>
    </div>
    <div class="time-item">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11a7 7 0 01-7 7m0 0a7 7 0 01-7-7m7 7v4m0 0H8m4 0h4m-4-8a3 3 0 01-3-3V5a3 3 0 116 0v6a3 3 0 01-3 3z"/>
      </svg>
      <span>Speaking time:</span>
      <span class="time-value" id="speaking-time">0 min</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Actions -->
  <div class="tool-actions" style="margin-top: var(--space-4);">
    <button id="copy-text" class="btn btn-secondary">Copy Text</button>
    <button id="load-sample" class="btn btn-text btn-sm">Load Sample</button>
    <button id="clear-text" class="btn btn-ghost">Clear</button>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="content-section">
  <h2>How to Use</h2>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step"><div class="step-number">1</div><div class="step-content"><h3>Enter Your Text</h3><p>Type or paste your text into the input area above.</p></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-number">2</div><div class="step-content"><h3>See Instant Results</h3><p>Word count, character count, and other statistics update in real-time.</p></div></div>
    <div class="step"><div class="step-number">3</div><div class="step-content"><h3>Check Time Estimates</h3><p>See how long it takes to read or speak your text aloud.</p></div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <h2>About Word Counter</h2>
  <p><strong>Word Counter</strong> is a free online tool that counts words, characters, sentences, and paragraphs in your text. It also provides reading time and speaking time estimates.</p>
  <p>This tool is perfect for writers, students, journalists, and anyone who needs to meet word count requirements for essays, articles, social media posts, or other content.</p>

  <h3>Key Features</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Word Count</strong> - Total number of words in your text</li>
    <li><strong>Character Count</strong> - Total characters including spaces</li>
    <li><strong>Characters (no spaces)</strong> - Characters excluding spaces</li>
    <li><strong>Sentence Count</strong> - Number of sentences detected</li>
    <li><strong>Paragraph Count</strong> - Number of paragraphs</li>
    <li><strong>Reading Time</strong> - Based on average reading speed (200 WPM)</li>
    <li><strong>Speaking Time</strong> - Based on average speaking speed (150 WPM)</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <h2>FAQ</h2>
  <div class="faq-list">
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">How is reading time calculated?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>Reading time is calculated based on an average reading speed of 200 words per minute, which is typical for adult readers.</p></div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">How is speaking time calculated?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>Speaking time uses an average of 150 words per minute, which is a comfortable speaking pace for presentations.</p></div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">Is my text saved or stored?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>No. All processing happens in your browser. Your text never leaves your device.</p></div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary class="faq-question">What counts as a word?</summary>
      <div class="faq-answer"><p>A word is any sequence of characters separated by spaces or line breaks. Numbers and hyphenated words count as single words.</p></div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-section">
  <h2>Related Tools</h2>
  <div class="related-tools">
    {% for tool in tools %}
    {% if tool.id != toolId %}
    <a href="/tools/{{ tool.id }}/" class="related-tool-link">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" width="16" height="16">{{ tool.icon | safe }}</svg>
      {{ tool.name }}
    </a>
    {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
